text: There are several lakes named Mud Lake within the U.S. state of Georgia. * Mud Lake, Camden County, Georgia. * Mud Lake, Charlton County, Georgia. * Mud Lake, Lowndes County, Georgia. * Mud Lake, Ware County, Georgia. ==References== * USGS-U.S. Board on Geographic Names Category:Lakes of Georgia (U.S. state)
title: Mud Lake (Georgia)
